description:
The Alien Fembot has completely destroyed Ashley 3000 circuits and she must be programmed from the ground up. Her evil master Ming will have her sent to the Magnetron if she does not succeed. All seemed to be going well with her seduction program until Ashley 3000’s programming encounters a conflict error and the tables turn drastically. Ashley 3000’s original programming is restored and she shoots the Alien Fembot with her Boobie Blasters and the Alien Fembot freezes. Now it’s Ashley 3000’s turn to reprogram the Alien and in order to do that she must directly plug into her. They must be connected to each other for this to work. And if it does, their sexual programming will be become one!
